==用途==
早在古代，[[真菌|真菌]]和[[细菌|细菌]]中的脂酶就已经在[[酸奶|酸奶]]和[[奶酪|奶酪]]的[[发酵|发酵]]过程中发挥作用。在现代社会中，脂酶则作为便宜而又多用途的降解脂类的高效催化剂而得以广泛使用。例如，一家[[生物技术|生物技术]]公司推出重组的脂酶，其可用于洗涤剂甚至作为制造[[可替代能源|可替代能源]]（将植物油转化为燃料）中的催化剂。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en |authors = Guo Z, Xu X |title=New opportunity for enzymatic modification of fats and oils with industrial potentials|journal=Org Biomol Chem|volume=3|issue=14 |pages=2615–9 |year=2005 |pmid=15999195 |doi=10.1039/b506763d }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en |authors=Gupta R, Gupta N, Rathi P |title=Bacterial lipases: an overview of production, purification and biochemical properties |journal=Appl Microbiol Biotechnol |volume=64 |issue=6 |pages=763–81 |year=2004 |pmid=14966663 |doi=10.1007/s00253-004-1568-8 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en |authors=Ban K, Kaieda M, Matsumoto T, Kondo A, Fukuda H |title=Whole cell biocatalyst for biodiesel fuel production utilizing Rhizopus oryzae cells immobilized within biomass support particles|journal=Biochem Eng J|volume=8|issue=1|pages=39–43|year=2001|pmid=11356369 |doi=10.1016/S1369-703X(00)00133-9 }}</ref>

